{"tid":1975850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【成功爭取】無口罩就拒絕照顧武肺人，護士堅守權益！","createTime":"2020-04-16T22:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T06:31:16.000Z","uid":202464,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4558bec7b1fea090a791504bfb2823051c4978d0","tid":1975850,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T22:42:01.000Z","msg":"1. 聖莫尼卡(Santa Monica)一間醫院向護士指出，大部份武漢肺炎個案毋須N95口罩，因此只提供普通外科口罩。<br />\n<br />\n2. 護士因此表明不會進入有懷疑感染武肺病人的病房。院方把其中10人停職調查，期間仍有薪。<br />\n<br />\n3. 事件引起爭議示威，院方最後宣佈所有醫護人員若須處理武肺，都會獲發N95口罩。<br />\n<br />\n4. 一位被停職護士說，這是一場勝利，值得高興，但事情發展至此亦令人感到憤怒，因為原來醫護的安全並非院方的首要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約每日新聞》"},{"pid":"b65c0bbd5a33c3ed829eca80018bb9fffbfcfabb","tid":1975850,"uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T22:43:43.000Z","msg":"港豬護士：<br />\n<br />\n「放唔低病人、要供樓不了、最緊要返工&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"4af124f3e44217bea14d4e32ef386e27e8deca5c","tid":1975850,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1cb410794c1b7882af96760d129799063ba00b","tid":1975850,"uid":47208,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b65c0bbd5a33c3ed829eca80018bb9fffbfcfabb","tid":1975850,"uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T22:43:43.000Z","msg":"港豬護士：<br />\n<br />\n「放唔低病人、要供樓不了、最緊要返工&hellip;&hellip;」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T00:24:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛<br />\n不推文</span></span>"},{"pid":"2dfa439567eb4521af9ecbdc80101095856f222f","tid":1975850,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4b1cb410794c1b7882af96760d129799063ba00b","tid":1975850,"uid":47208,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b65c0bbd5a33c3ed829eca80018bb9fffbfcfabb","tid":1975850,"uid":202464,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T22:43:43.000Z",